00:27:09,146 --> 00:27:12,527
done versus have you played my game? Cool, well it's a 60 hour experience and you can

643
00:27:12,547 --> 00:27:15,789
start off, uh, in the first town or whatever and, you know, people don't have the time

644
00:27:15,829 --> 00:27:21,132
for that. Um, so explore the system, uh, with each piece that you're making, uh, but keep

645
00:27:21,172 --> 00:27:22,993
everything moving so that it stays interesting.

646
00:27:24,082 --> 00:27:26,302
And then lastly, especially for younger game developers,

647
00:27:26,382 --> 00:27:28,322
I trust that the process will build your style

