00:27:31,343 --> 00:27:33,043
we're making things, we're making a lot of things,

651
00:27:33,123 --> 00:27:34,724
and we're not really concerned about the outcome

652
00:27:34,764 --> 00:27:36,884
of how good they are, if they're gonna make a lot of money,

653
00:27:37,184 --> 00:27:39,565
or anything, we're just focused on this small little piece.

